data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE UP TO $17,600.00 to BUY DOWN RATE for 2 years when buyer closes with Seller approved lender. Don't miss this on this beautiful custom built farmhouse sitting on 9.8 acres located off 48 with easy access to 75 between Tampa and Ocala is move in ready. This home has 4 bedrooms and 5 full baths. The home boasts soaring 18 foot ceilings with an incredible kitchen overlooking the yard and the Lily pond. This home has a split floor plan with a master on one side and all the guest rooms on the other. The master, which is on the second floor, has a large walk-in closet with a side room that could be an office or a nursery with a large master bath with a massive soaking tub. There is a steam shower and a dumb waiter for your laundry down to the main floor. The guest room which is on the other side of the house has one large room on the second floor with an attached full bath. The other two bedrooms downstairs have a full bath between them. The massive fireplace is the center of the great room and shares the space of the kitchen and dining table. The farmhouse kitchen has granite counter tops and plenty of cabinets with a large walk in pantry. There is a full bath in the laundry room and another full bath in the garage. The home has a central vacuum system, new water heater in 2022 and a whole house generator for lost electricity. The home has a screened in porch off the den and a large wrap around porch almost around the entire house. The oversized (4) car garage has plenty of space for cars and for storage. The property has a running stream with a bridge going out to the large pond on the front of the house. The pond has plenty of fish and lilies which are beautiful when blooming. The farm has a chicken coop and two large sheds for your use. The property has 3 wells and a large fenced in paddock for larger animals with a 3 stall pole barn with storage.
